{"tid":501146,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"聖誕節梗係玩minecraft 做毒撚?","createTime":"2017-12-16T14:01:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-26T15:50:30.000Z","uid":66938,"like":5,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1b583b72639add4b801281e05128dd53f8a03204","tid":501146,"uid":66938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T14:01:23.000Z","msg":"聖誕節長假好悶<br />\nPS4 又唔想玩, 但係又想休閒鳩fing下?<br />\n我地lihk9fingfing 絕對係你首選<br />\n我地係一個輕鬆hea鳩鳩既休閒生存ser<br />\n歡迎各路巴打一齊入黎鳩fing fing <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話說呢個ser 係舊ser重製而成, <br />\n所以會見到好多現成傳送門係spawn但係又未開放住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然而家minecraft 最新係 1.12.2,<br />\n但係因為plugin 未更新哂上去, 所以<br />\nversion 是 <span style=\"color: orange;\">1.12</span><br />\n有白名單,請留下你的名字 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後一般既essential plugins 都有<br />\n之後有<span style=\"color: orange;\">資源世界,</span>希望大家盡量去番資源世界挖野<br />\n一開波生存起家挖少少無咩所謂<br />\n盡量唔好挖太爛就ok, OP有d強逼症<br />\n<br />\n各種farm會係大家玩到咁上下就開始起,<br />\n大家唔洗再愁無材料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n設定<br />\n1. 防火防爆防跌裝, creeper 同TNT會爆炸,會有傷害,但唔會爆到block<br />\n<br />\n2. 一般既大路指令都有,<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">/spawn /sethome /home /tpa /bal </span>等等<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">每人可以set 5 個home, set唔同世界都得</span><br />\n<br />\n3. 有<span style=\"color: teal;\"> /co i </span>可以check 箱有無俾人偷野<br />\n亦有lockette 可以鎖箱share箱俾特定人士<br />\n<br />\n4. SPAWN 有 傳送門 區域<br />\n送你直達不同世界既角落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5. 有經濟系統,可以用<span style=\"color: teal;\">/bal</span> 睇<br />\n新人入ser都會拎到 <span style=\"color: gold;\">$5000</span><br />\n賺錢除左同玩家交易之外,亦可以賣野俾ser<br />\nser 係無限收你d垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n努力挖垃圾賣 富可敵國不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n6. 有<span style=\"color: pink;\">Lift plugin </span>, 只要兩個木牌,兩粒制,一個鐵磚,一塊玻璃 就可以<br />\n高度限制都係3格先起到部Lift<br />\n<br />\n7. 有<span style=\"color: red;\">紅石連閃限制</span><br />\n<br />\n8. 為方便各位hea鳩鳩, 現設新手包助你更加輕鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n暫時唔會有創造世界<br />\n<br />\n紅石方面,由於server仲係細ser<br />\nRAM數有限,請大家自律建設<br />\n盡量唔好有大型紅石/連閃<br />\n亦唔好騷擾到其他玩家<br />\n多謝合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nsub domain : <a href=\"http://lihk.mcph.co\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flihk.mcph.co&d=C0HKt4MF2W2ykmPSQtzfJU4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=e033014a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihk.mcph.co</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家有discord group<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/sXKC37E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FsXKC37E&d=C0HKt4MF2W2ykmPSQtzfJU4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=21cce8f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/sXKC37E</a><br />\n有大量資訊係入面<br />\n唔用mic 都可以睇到<br />\n齊來吹水吧"},{"pid":"f606cb76594a5072da060eb602abf64efcbc8e50","tid":501146,"uid":64318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T14:03:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22413690b59fbea7339d13e442117cb524afc414","tid":501146,"uid":66938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T14:03:38.000Z","msg":"講番少少規則先<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請到資源世界挖礦<br />\n請勿在主世界挖礦!!!<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n1. 都係自律就好, 唔好亂搞人地d屋/騷擾到人就好<br />\n<br />\n2. 終界要塞由大家自行發掘<br />\n只要發現到, OP 就會開番spawn 個終界傳部門 (而家無開到)<br />\n咁到時候就唔洗走好遠先入到終界<br />\n<br />\n3. 終界既第一條終界龍總會有人特別想爭<br />\n但係始終係鳩hea ser, 所以希望大家可以share 條龍一齊打<br />\n你想要龍蛋唔緊要, 如果你係第一個搵到要塞既<br />\n可以同OP講,我留番粒龍蛋俾你<br />\n但係龍就希望share番一齊打<br />\n<br />\n4. 下界門請自己開<br />\nspawn 都有個下界既門, 會係多少少人個陣就會開<br />\n同樣地, 而家都係未開放<br />\n但通常大家都整一個係自己屋企, 所以其實分別都不大<br />\n<br />\n5. 主世界既地底係無任何洞, 所以唔會有怪生<br />\n因此地面就會好多怪, 有番d挑戰性<br />\n<br />\n6. 亦因為咁主世界無生怪磚<br />\n生怪磚請到資源世界發掘<br />\n一但搵到既, 請通知op<br />\nOP會陸續開放公家farm俾大家(會有portal傳去)<br />\n咁大家都可以儉番起既心力<br />\n<br />\n7. 因為呢個ser係舊ser重製而成,<br />\n所以基本上一切應該有既farm/portal 其實都齊哂<br />\n(slime/blaze/enderman 個d都會有)<br />\n只不過一開始唔會完全開放哂<br />\n會因應人數同玩家進度陸續開放番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n8. 最後係admin團隊保留一切既最終決定權<br />\n如果有犯錯既,會先jail 你幾分鐘, 如果嚴重/再犯就會直接ban<br />\n請大家自律玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"126b8da6b3c95680ac496a83e5ee4259a61d8353","tid":501146,"uid":66938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T14:04:57.000Z","msg":"最後當然係補少少圖啦<br />\n<br />\nSpawn : 天空之城<br />\n入面有官方商店, 亦開放左位置俾玩家進駐<br />\n有哂傳送門送大家到各mob farm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/152416_0a15afc49252258b6e7c0821c3499d3d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F152416_0a15afc49252258b6e7c0821c3499d3d.png&h=c43b869b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/152432_36bbb1d437f452add62d3bf604c43334.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F152432_36bbb1d437f452add62d3bf604c43334.png&h=c76afc94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/152447_a0fc2c4834bcc34a00d09ff3ea9b335f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F152447_a0fc2c4834bcc34a00d09ff3ea9b335f.png&h=82edc059&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/152454_adda57714903bd673a766219c55e39a8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F152454_adda57714903bd673a766219c55e39a8.png&h=63423813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n資源世界 - 沙漠之都, 沙城<br />\n資源世界座落係數種不同生態既區既交界<br />\n有沙漠/平原/高山 等等, 想挖咩都係哂左近<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/214712_fb5c81ed3a220004b71069645f112867.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F214712_fb5c81ed3a220004b71069645f112867.png&h=ec8731a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主世界(生存世界) <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/214619_812749e1a307f38fd0a88b54bea55ff2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F214619_812749e1a307f38fd0a88b54bea55ff2.png&h=d5c782c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n垃圾回收場<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/214622_8266e4bfeda1bd42d8f9794eb4ea0a13.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F214622_8266e4bfeda1bd42d8f9794eb4ea0a13.png&h=dad97beb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家主世界一間屋都未有<br />\n仲唔快d黎插旗仔宣示主權!?"},{"pid":"494c8d2b735e4a993f1d9b46b5a5069fb981316d","tid":501146,"uid":66938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T14:05:26.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj